Activity overview overlay key remap

    gsettings set org.gnome.mutter overlay-key 'Alt_L'

* * *

Ubuntu switch language shortcut Alt + /

    gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.wm.keybindings switch-input-source "['<Alt>slash']"
    gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.wm.keybindings switch-input-source-backward "['<Alt>slash']"

* * *

# Kivy installation does not find GL/gl.h
Solution - https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10283465/kivy-installation-does-not-find-gl-gl-h
sudo apt install libgl1-mesa-dev
